        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " to this effect. “You do not believe your own theory; you know as well as I how absurd it is, and that I must be casting out devils by a very different spirit from Beelzebub. You are therefore not merely mistaken ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
